column5: St. Kitts and Nevis Affected Exports to the USA (Top 100)
DESCRIPTION
Plugs and sockets, for a voltage not exceeding 1,000 volts.
Articles of jewellery and parts thereof, of precious metal (other tha silver or gold), whether or not plated or clad with precious metal.
Bank and currency notes.

Live monkeys.

Sets or assortments of gaskets and similar joints, dissimilar in composition, put up in pouches, envelopes or similar packings.

Parts suitable for use solely or principally with compression-ignition internal combustion piston engines (diesel or semi-diesel engines), other than those for road motor vehicles or for marine craft.
Bicycles and other cycles, not motorized, not for the transport of goods.
